{{Messianic Judaism}} [[Messianic Judaism]] is a [[syncretic]] [[religion|religious movement]] that arose in the 1960s and 1970s. It is a mixture of [[Judaism|Jewish]] symbols and [[Christian theology]] (itself derivative of ancient Jewish theology). Its believers are technically Christians.
